Duke replaces Kruk as head of the Ninja Monkey Guards of Marim after the events of Monkey Madness II. He can be spoken to post-quest to receive 2 x 50,000 XP rewards in Magic, Ranged, Attack, Defence, Strength, or Hitpoints. He can be found on the east hill above the main gate of Ape Atoll. This hill can be reached by walking up the west hill and climbing up the ladder to access a bridge leading to the east hill.

'''Duke''' replaces [[Kruk]] as head of the [[Monkey Guard (ninja)|Ninja Monkey Guards]] of [[Marim]] after the events of [[Monkey Madness II]]. He can be spoken to post-quest to receive 2 x 50,000 XP rewards in [[Magic]], [[Ranged]], [[Attack]], [[Defence]], [[Strength]], or [[Hitpoints]]. He can be found on the east hill above the main gate of [[Ape Atoll]]. This hill can be reached by walking up the west hill and climbing up the ladder to access a bridge leading to the east hill.
